## Penerapan CLT

transformasi random_normal2 menjadi normal standar (berlaku untuk distribusi kontinu apapun -> sampling dist.)

gunakan CLT -> scale


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
par(mfrow = c(1,2))
plot(density(random_normal2), main = "Sebelum")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](modul3_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-20-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(density(scale(random_normal2)), main = "Sesudah")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](modul3_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-21-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
